	<LINE>THE GRAHAM FREE SCHOOL.</LINE>
	<LINE>The late Mrs. Janet Graham, or Lindsay, left a</LINE>
	<LINE>fund to be applied among other purposes for the</LINE>
	<LINE>education of the children of deserving parents, bear-</LINE>
	<LINE>ing the names of Graham, "Norrie, " or " Norris."</LINE>
